      <title>贝莱德正在洽谈出售 Sperry 旗下 Authentic Brands Group 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/blackrock-is-in-talks-to-sell-stake-in-sperry-owner-authentic-brands-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，包括 CVC Capital Partners、General Atlantic、HPS Investment Partners 和 Leonard Green &amp; Partners 在内的投资者集团正在就收购贝莱德公司在 Authentic Brands Group 的股权进行洽谈。]]></description>
